move1.name: Tackle
move1.description: A physical attack in which the user charges and slams into the target with its whole body.

move2.name: Rock Throw
move2.description: The user throws rocks at the target to inflict damage.

move3.name: Magnitude
move3.description: The user creates a ground-shaking tremor to deal damage. The power of this move varies.

move4.name: Rock Slide
move4.description: Large boulders are hurled at the opposing team to inflict damage. It may also make the targets flinch.
